Assalam Mualaikum. 
Dulang Ambeng Royal (4pax).
Thank you @singaporeliciouz for the surprised dinner. The portion was really huge!!! My family enjoyed eating this Ambeng so much. 
SEDAP 😋 .
.

Includes: - Nasi - Ayam Lemak Cili Padi
- Daging Rendang
- Sambal Goreng
- Terong Belado
- Paru Goreng Rempah
- Begerdil
- Serunding
- Sambal Kacang Ikan Bilis
- Udang Belado Hijau
- Urap
- Ikan Kering
- Sambal Belacan .
